'''anthracene'''
#{{chemistry}} a [[tricyclic]] [[aromatic]] [[hydrocarbon]] (an [[acene]] containg two fused rings) obtained from [[coal tar]]; used in the manufacture of wood [[preservative]]s, [[insecticide]]s and the [[dye]] [[alizarin]]; it is [[isomeric]] with [[phenanthrene]]